snippet.title: GO VACATION - Overview Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Gather your friends and let’s go on vacation! GO VACATION launches July 27th on Nintendo Switch.

You can pre-order the game from the official GO VACATION website:
https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch/GO-VACATION-1381935.html?utm_medium=social&utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=GoVacation%7Cw27
